; SAT: (x XOR y) == (x + y) AND (x AND y) != 0 for 12-bit x, y
; XOR == ADD when no carries (AND==0), but also when carries wrap mod 2^12
; e.g. x=y=2048: XOR=0, ADD=4096 mod 4096=0, AND=2048!=0
; Domain: 4096^2 = 16M — tests multi-variable blast
; Expected: SAT
1 sort bitvec 12
2 sort bitvec 1
3 input 1 x
4 input 1 y
5 xor 1 3 4
6 add 1 3 4
7 eq 2 5 6
8 and 1 3 4
9 zero 1
10 neq 2 8 9
11 and 2 7 10
12 bad 11
